title: G.I. Joe: Resolute
overview: The G.I. Joe team work to prevent Cobra from destroying the world. Snake Eyes confronts Storm Shadow, Scarlett and Duke attempt stop Cobra, Roadblock and Gung-Ho encounter Destro and the Baroness. The Resolute cartoon is a series of 10 five-minute webisodes to be capped off by a 10-minute finale.Â
